rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Yeeeugh! My fur's all sticky from the
machine oil!

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0002
rows.name:
All I did was squeeze through a gap
in some thingamabob, and now I'm
a walking grease monster!

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Now my beautiful glossy fur is reduced
to horrible sticky clumps, and it smells
something awful too!

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Aww, thanks for the concern. But I'll
be fine. A quick dip in the hot springs
and I'll be silky smooth again.

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It's so much fun swimming about in
there when there's no one around.
Just don't tell the humans!
